            <title>[FLINK-19971] flink-connector-hbase-base depends on hbase-server, instead of hbase-client</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-19971</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;flink-connector-hbase-base depends on hbase-server, instead of hbase-client and hbase-common.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I believe hbase-server is only needed for starting a Minicluster and therefore should be in the test scope.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This was introduced by &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-1928&quot; title=&quot;BlobManager can be a bottleneck on large deployments&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLINK-1928&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLINK-1928&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
